 ('5', '6', '4', '1', 'en_nz', '1', NULL, '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Home\",\"slug\":\"home\",\"postDate\":1517480313,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":[]}', '2018-02-01 10:18:33', '2018-02-01 10:18:33', '8cb81c2f-cc75-455b-9414-ed5c72247be8'),
 ('6', '6', '4', '1', 'en_nz', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Home\",\"slug\":\"home\",\"postDate\":1517480313,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"12\":\"Hi, I\\u2019m Jenny \\u2014 web designer, bicycle rider, enthusiastic coder, snow lover & quiet achiever.\\r\\n\",\"14\":\"\",\"13\":\"\"}}', '2018-02-01 10:28:08', '2018-02-01 10:28:08', '5135534c-af1e-4c22-a9c4-756c16dd29cb'),
 ('7', '7', '3', '1', 'en_nz', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Frontal Lobe\",\"slug\":\"frontal-lobe\",\"postDate\":1517480989,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"5\":\"\",\"8\":\"Frontal Lobe is an up and coming business who came to Big Boy Websites for a website to showcase what they have to offer \\u2014 designing and building beautiful, sustainable designs using bamboo and scrap wood.\",\"11\":\"\",\"6\":\"\",\"9\":\"The website was broken down into the different sections required \\u2014 information about the team, an online shop, contact information and links to their social media. This information combined with beautiful, high-quality imagery was able to convey the company ethos.\",\"4\":\"Web Design\",\"7\":\"\",\"10\":\"With the launch of the website, Frontal Lobe was able to make their mark as a progressive, socially-minded business based on sustainability and have an online outlet for their creations.\"}}', '2018-02-01 10:29:49', '2018-02-01 10:29:49', 'c21997bf-041b-4ca6-a436-4d0b9302bd7e'),
 ('8', '6', '4', '1', 'en_nz', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Home\",\"slug\":\"home\",\"postDate\":1517480313,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"12\":\"Hi, I\\u2019m Jenny \\u2014 web designer, bicycle rider, enthusiastic coder, snow lover & quiet achiever.\\r\\n\",\"14\":\"\",\"13\":\"\"}}', '2018-02-01 10:30:42', '2018-02-01 10:30:42', '7157e039-464d-4c73-adbd-64ab97c2cab4'),
 ('9', '7', '3', '1', 'en_nz', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Frontal Lobe\",\"slug\":\"frontal-lobe\",\"postDate\":1517480940,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"5\":\"\",\"8\":\"Frontal Lobe is an up and coming business who came to Big Boy Websites for a website to showcase what they have to offer \\u2014 designing and building beautiful, sustainable designs using bamboo and scrap wood.\",\"11\":\"\",\"6\":\"\",\"9\":\"The website was broken down into the different sections required \\u2014 information about the team, an online shop, contact information and links to their social media. This information combined with beautiful, high-quality imagery was able to convey the company ethos.\",\"4\":\"Web Design\",\"7\":\"\",\"10\":\"With the launch of the website, Frontal Lobe was able to make their mark as a progressive, socially-minded business based on sustainability and have an online outlet for their creations.\"}}', '2018-02-02 04:51:53', '2018-02-02 04:51:53', '78b01805-ff1d-4002-b043-5a22c1af137e'),
 ('10', '8', '3', '1', 'en_nz', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Bruncher\",\"slug\":\"bruncher\",\"postDate\":1517547170,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"5\":\"\",\"8\":\"In post-quake Christchurch, I often found myself spending far too much of my time driving around the CBD hoping to find a cafe that was open for Brunch. That\\u2019s why I created Bruncher.\",\"11\":\"\",\"6\":\"\",\"9\":\"When designing Bruncher it was important that the app gave real-time information on nearby cafes, with open\\/close information, detailed directions and was easy to use on mobile devices. \\r\\n\\r\\nUsing the Google Maps Javascript API in conjunction with the Materialise CSS framework I was able to do all these things.\",\"4\":\"Google Maps API, UI, Materialize\",\"7\":\"\",\"10\":\"The app has an easy-to-use interface which allows users to locate local cafes via geolocation or manual input and determine whether they are open or closed. The app also offers the users detailed directions and is responsive across a range of devices.\"}}', '2018-02-02 04:52:50', '2018-02-02 04:52:50', 'f9ea58a3-cfe7-417b-a5eb-4e151eabe505'),
 ('11', '9', '3', '1', 'en_nz', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"The Perfect Pour\",\"slug\":\"the-perfect-pour\",\"postDate\":1517547232,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"5\":\"\",\"8\":\"While there are a lot of websites that review cafes, the emphasis is often on the overall cafe experience as opposed to the quality of the coffee served. The Perfect Pour is a website where users can register an account and leave reviews about the coffee at local cafes.\",\"11\":\"\",\"6\":\"\",\"9\":\"In order to create a review website, it was important that the site was able to handle a variety of different modes of functionality. The website is a basic CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) app built using PHP with no framework. \\r\\n\",\"4\":\"PHP, Bootstrap, CRUD\",\"7\":\"\",\"10\":\"The site is styled using a heavily customised Bootstrap which allows the site to maintain responsiveness across different device widths so users can leave reviews while they are on-the-go.\"}}', '2018-02-02 04:53:52', '2018-02-02 04:53:52', 'c866bd4d-03d2-48ce-8e7c-e0133c392e2b'),
 ('12', '10', '3', '1', 'en_nz', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Forest Karts\",\"slug\":\"forest-karts\",\"postDate\":1517547278,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"5\":\"\",\"8\":\"Forest Karts came to Big Boy Websites with an exciting new business project \\u2014 outdoor go-karting in a picturesque Canterbury forest location. As a new business, they needed a website to show potential customers what they have to offer.\",\"11\":\"\",\"6\":\"\",\"9\":\"The website design was broken down into different sections \\u2014 go-karting packages on offer, health and safety information, a reliable way to contact them and information about the team behind Forest Karts.\",\"4\":\"Web Design\",\"7\":\"\",\"10\":\"With the brief in hand, I created a fun and informative website that reflected the business they were in. Lots of fun little design details combined with forest and go-kart imagery complete with a mobile site to ensure accessibility on the go.\"}}', '2018-02-02 04:54:38', '2018-02-02 04:54:38', 'bef91b4e-0479-465c-9ec9-98d2a40ed94a'),
 ('13', '11', '3', '1', 'en_nz', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Natalie Rose Photography\",\"slug\":\"natalie-rose-photography\",\"postDate\":1517547337,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"5\":\"\",\"8\":\"Natalie is a young Christchurch-based photographer with a passion for shooting astrophotography and local events. She needed a website to showcase her talents, sell prints and a way for potential customers to get in contact. \",\"11\":\"\",\"6\":\"\",\"9\":\"As Natalie is a freelance photographer it was important that she was able to self-manage the content on the site and upload new images to her portfolio as required. It was clear that in order to do this a CMS was required.\",\"4\":\"WordPress Development, WooCommerce \",\"7\":\"\",\"10\":\"In order to give her a customisable site, I created a one-of-a-kind Wordpress template which allows her to self-manage the WooCommerce shop and make updates to all aspects of the site as needed. \"}}', '2018-02-02 04:55:37', '2018-02-02 04:55:37', '58789972-25dd-45a8-a9f4-920ad978dc0e'),
 ('14', '12', '3', '1', 'en_nz', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"tasman.io\",\"slug\":\"tasman-io\",\"postDate\":1517547381,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"5\":\"\",\"8\":\"Custom D had been working on an in-house task management app for quite a while and it was now time to gather public interest about the upcoming Beta launch of the application.\",\"11\":\"\",\"6\":\"\",\"9\":\"We designed a one-page SilverStripe website to attract beta testers which gave details about the product on offer and the range of benefits that it would provide small businesses.\",\"4\":\"SilverStripe, MailChimp, Web Design\",\"7\":\"\",\"10\":\"In order to gather public interest, a simple input field was added to the site for users to subscribe. The input field linked to a MailChimp mail list where users were regularly updated with the latest information regarding the Beta release of the app.\"}}', '2018-02-02 04:56:22', '2018-02-02 04:56:22', 'e2ea5475-47a0-41b0-9e34-1093ea3614ec'),
