 ('11', 'field', '8', 'en_nz', ' natalie is a young christchurch based photographer with a passion for shooting astrophotography and local events she needed a website to showcase her talents sell prints and a way for potential customers to get in contact '),
 ('11', 'field', '6', 'en_nz', ' group 4nrp '),
